:76"><span class="vo"><span class="vb">﴿</span><span class="v" data-v="43:76" id="qr-wahidi-asbab-43-76">وَمَا ظَلَمْنَاهُمْ وَلَٰكِن كَانُوا هُمُ الظَّالِمِينَ</span><a class="vn" href="/quran/43/76" target="_blank" title="سورة الزخرف"></a><span class="ve">﴾</span></span><div class="tafsir"><p id="102.15C8C"/><p id="102.cDDEb"/><p id="102.B2822"/></div></div><div class="verse-tafsir" data-verse="43:77"><span class="vo"><span class="vb">﴿</span><span class="v" data-v="43:77" id="qr-wahidi-asbab-43-77">وَنَادَوْا يَا مَالِكُ لِيَقْضِ عَلَيْنَا رَبُّكَ ۖ قَالَ إِنَّكُم مَّاكِثُونَ</span><a class="vn" href="/quran/43/77" target="_blank" title="سورة الزخرف"></a><span class="ve">﴾</span></span><div class="tafsir"><p id="102.a31E7"/><p id="102.b3E1B"/><p id="102.Ddf53"/></div></div><div class="verse-tafsir" data-verse="43:78"><span class="vo"><span class="vb">﴿</span><span class="v" data-v="43:78" id="qr-wahidi-asbab-43-78">لَقَدْ جِئْنَاكُم بِالْحَقِّ وَلَٰكِنَّ أَكْثَرَكُمْ لِلْحَقِّ كَارِهُونَ</span><a class="vn" href="/quran/43/78" target="_blank" title="سورة الزخرف"></a><span class="ve">﴾</span></span><div class="tafsir"><p id="102.EABeB"/><p id="102.684E9"/><p id="102.2aD98"/></div></div><div class="verse-tafsir" data-verse="43:79"><span class="vo"><span class="vb">﴿</span><span class="v" data-v="43:79" id="qr-wahidi-asbab-43-79">أَمْ أَبْرَمُوا أَمْرًا فَإِنَّا مُبْرِمُونَ</span><a class="vn" href="/quran/43/79" target="_blank" title="سورة الزخرف"></a><span class="ve">﴾</span></span><div class="tafsir"><p id="102.25eF8"/><p id="102.Df77d"/><p id="102.BF77A"/></div></div><div class="verse-tafsir" data-verse="43:80"><span class="vo"><span class="vb">﴿</span><span class="v" data-v="43:80" id="qr-wahidi-asbab-43-80">أَمْ يَحْسَبُونَ أَنَّا لَا نَسْمَعُ سِرَّهُمْ وَنَجْوَاهُم ۚ بَلَىٰ وَرُسُلُنَا لَدَيْهِمْ يَكْتُبُونَ</span><a class="vn" href="/quran/43/80" target="_blank" title="سورة الزخرف"></a><span class="ve">﴾</span></span><div class="tafsir"><p id="102.c9d98